buildCommand: curl -L https://storage.googleapis.com/flutter_infra_release/releases/stable/linux/flutter_linux_3.24.1-stable.tar.xz | tar -xJ && export PATH=$PATH:$PWD/flutter/bin && flutter config --enable-web && flutter pub get && flutter build web --release --web-renderer html --base-href=/
installCommand: curl -L https://storage.googleapis.com/flutter_infra_release/releases/stable/linux/flutter_linux_3.24.1-stable.tar.xz | tar -xJ && export PATH=$PATH:$PWD/flutter/bin && flutter config --enable-web
